[size=6][b][img]https://www.kdau.com/ScryingOrb/icon.png[/img] Scrying Orb[/b][/size]

[i]a [url=http://stardewvalley.net/]Stardew Valley[/url] mod by [url=https://www.kdau.com]kdau[/url][/i]

Craft a Scrying Orb with a recipe from Welwick and you too can peer into the future. Make an offering to the spirits to scry mining conditions, geode contents, rare events, garbage loot and more.

This mod is based on the [url=https://mouseypounds.github.io/stardew-predictor/]Stardew Predictor[/url] web app by MouseyPounds, whose tools are all worth a look. Its companion mod, [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/stardewvalley/mods/5605]Public Access TV[/url], offers a different route to much of the same information for the current game day.

[size=4][b][img alt="Compatibility"]https://www.kdau.com/headers/compatibility.png[/img][/b][/size]

[b]Game:[/b] Stardew Valley 1.5.3+ (predictions may be wrong for any future 1.6)

[b]Platform:[/b] Linux, macOS or Windows (Android: use 1.4 version)

[b]Multiplayer:[/b] works; every player must install

[b]Other mods:[/b] There are no known outright conflicts. These mods are handled specially:

[list]
[*][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/stardewvalley/mods/4171]Better Garbage Cans[/url]: This mod's garbage predictions are hidden.
[*][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/stardewvalley/mods/3753]Stardew Valley Expanded[/url]: This mod correctly reflects the different arrangement of garbage cans.
[*][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/stardewvalley/mods/4330]Witchy Crystal Farm 2.0[/url]: This mod makes the sculpture on the farm a working Scrying Orb.
[/list]
If any of your other mods affect the areas this mod covers, the orb may make incorrect predictions. If you would like me to add support for another mod, please open an issue [url=https://gitlab.com/kdau/predictivemods/-/issues]on GitLab[/url] or discuss it in the thread here.

[size=4][b][img alt="Installation"]https://www.kdau.com/headers/installation.png[/img][/b][/size]

[list=1]
[*]Install [url=https://smapi.io/]SMAPI[/url]
[*]Install [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/stardewvalley/mods/1720]Json Assets[/url]
[*]Install [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/stardewvalley/mods/5098]Generic Mod Config Menu[/url] (optional, for easier configuration)
[*]Download this mod from the link in the header above
