[size=4][b][img alt="Configuration"]https://www.kdau.com/headers/configuration.png[/img][/b][/size]

If you have installed Generic Mod Config Menu, you can access this mod's configuration by clicking the cogwheel button at the lower left corner of the Stardew Valley title screen and then choosing "Scrying Orb".

Otherwise, you can edit this mod's [icode]config.json[/icode] file. It will be created in the mod's main folder ([icode]Mods/ScryingOrb[/icode]) the first time you run the game with the mod installed. These options are available:

[list]
[*][icode]InaccuratePredictions[/icode]: Set this to [icode]true[/icode] to let the spirits make predictions that are inaccurate due to game version mismatch and/or conflicting mods. For entertainment purposes only.
[*][icode]InstantRecipe[/icode]: Set this to [icode]true[/icode] to give the Scrying Orb crafting recipe immediately instead of needing two hearts with the Wizard.
[*][icode]UnlimitedUse[/icode]: Set this to [icode]true[/icode] to have the Scrying Orb work without taking offerings permanently.
[*][icode]ActivateKey[/icode]: Set this to any valid keybinding that will then activate the Scrying Orb unlimited use menu without any orb or offering. [url=https://stardewvalleywiki.com/Modding:Player_Guide/Key_Bindings#Available_bindings]See the list of keybindings here.[/url]
[/list]

[size=4][b][img alt="Translation"]https://www.kdau.com/headers/translation.png[/img][/b][/size]

This mod can be translated into any language supported by Stardew Valley. It is currently available in English, French, Portuguese, Russian and Simplified Chinese.

Your contribution would be welcome. Please see the [url=https://stardewvalleywiki.com/Modding:Translations]instructions on the wiki[/url]. You can send me your work in [url=https://gitlab.com/kdau/predictivemods/-/issues]a GitLab issue[/url] or a message here.

